fields.description:
HI,

We would like to upgrade BioHub Facial Dell VxRail HCI infrastructure as part of our maintenance activity.  We are not expecting any downtime, however there would be 10 minutes interruption can happen and we are doing this activity node by node.

 We are planning to upgrade the version from 7.0.2 à 7.0.401. Please help to get the approval to perform the activity.

fields.customfield_15109:
This patch released by Dell and recommends us to upgrade in the system.
We need to install this patches on stg/prod HCI as we hosted all environments in the same hardware.
fields.customfield_15107: We are planning to upgrade the VxRail version from 7.0.2 à 7.0.401. We are planning to perform the changes in all nodes. There will not be any downtime as we are upgrading the servers node by node. However,  10 minutes interruption can occur.
fields.customfield_15108: We will take the backup of the configuration and we can roll back the changes if any issue reporting.
